---
title: Blogroll
description: I've had the pleasure of meeting, knowing of, knowing personally, and spending great time with a lot of amazing people that have inspired me in different ways over my years on this Earth. Here are a handful of them.
full_width: true
---
{%- set collection = blogroll | keySort('title') -%}

<nav class=" [ grid ] [ shelf ] ">
{% for item in collection %}
	<article class=" [ flow ] ">
		<h1>
			<a href="{{ item.url }}" rel="{{ item.ref }}">
				{{ item.title | safe }}
				<br>
				<small aria-hidden="true">{{ item.url | getHost }}</small>
			</a>
		</h1>
	</article>
{% endfor %}
</nav>
